      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:7:3:27:3",
      "relations": null,
      "text": [
        " سَأَلْتُهُ عَنْ رَجُلٍ افْتَرَى عَلَى قَوْمٍ جَمَاعَةً قَالَ فَقَالَ إِنْ أَتَوْا بِهِ مُجْتَمِعِينَ ضُرِبَ حَدّاً وَاحِداً وَ إِنْ أَتَوْا بِهِ مُتَفَرِّقِينَ ضُرِبَ لِكُلِّ رَجُلٍ حَدّاً."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, form Muhammad Bin Isa, from Yunus, from Muhammad Bin Humran, ",
          "(The narrator) says, ‘I asked Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> about a man who fabricated upon a group of people. So he<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘If they come with it altogether, he would be whipped one Penalty (<span class=\"iTxt\">Hadd</span>), and if they come with it seperately, he would be whipped for each man, one Penalty (<span class=\"iTxt\">Hadd</span>)’."
        ]
      }
    }
